          "ANALYSIS": [
            {
              "pointer": "1",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "\"Conventional\" method: deriving the energy dependence",
                "of the cross section section SIG(E)  and  calculation",
                "reaction  rate  LAMBDA(T)  using equations connecting",
                "LANBDA,  SIG and number of photons with energy E  per",
                "unit volume and energy interval ng(E,T)."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "2",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "\"Superposition\" method:  approximating  the   thermal",
                "Planck  spectrum  ng(E,T) by superposition of several",
                "bremsstrahlung  spectra  with   different   end-point",
                "energies."
              ]
            }
